name: Games
body:
### What is this?
I thought I could just start off with a small description of this repisotry, in case anyone actually visits this page. The purpose of this repository is to publish my game development projects online just so people could play them and send me feedback. I will create everything from strategy, top-down RPG, side scrolling platformer. Some will be original work and some will be prototypes.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
